data.description: Bask in the open floorplan of this large beautifully updated traditional home. On top of the huge kitchen/dining/living space, this home boasts 6 bdrms + bonus rm upstairs + 2 addl rms on the main. A new roof, interior paint and updated 1/2 bath on the main help make this home sparkle. In an ideal location, this home backs to greenspace with immediate access to the Fanno Creek Trail and is just mins to Washington Square. Welcome Home!
